{"tid":1847761,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［無炒人］AIA: 要求經紀刪去帖文","createTime":"2020-01-28T07:48:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-28T07:52:15.000Z","uid":22556,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5b48ca520b93d59a35bf117514e76a5c6f933a1a","tid":1847761,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:48:21.000Z","msg":"昨日醫管局宣佈，豁免符合武漢肺炎呈報機制的非本地人收費，消息一出，全城嘩然，擔心大量內地人會湧港求診，加劇公立醫院負荷。不過，有部份保險經紀卻隨即在微博等社交平台「推波助瀾」，轉發醫管局消息之餘，更加上個人評論，大有呼籲內地人來港求醫的意味。有保險公司表示，已就事件要求經紀刪去帖文，以及作嚴重紀律處分，不排除停職。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158562114207448/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10158562114207448%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=ib6ZiIlk8HgX3sh0XBbtbw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=f2a5c322\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10158562114207448/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"4ecab6cd048bd71d468eace6c466e4fc3eabbd6d","tid":1847761,"uid":207553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d7f12153a9d97531051cdffba45cb11d74f3eb","tid":1847761,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-28T07:49:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">除咗醫護之外<br />\n垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">學校停 政府部門停 康文設施都停<br />\n啲人就湧晒去唔停嘅中心<br />\n社區爆發岌岌可危<br />\n<br />\n<ins>要求立即停止所有非緊急服務</ins></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"700faf7187f32f4529511f5cbf4229d3fc65977b","tid":1847761,"uid":317233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c